係要駁電 要入紙申請改動 驗車<br />\n裝之前工程師要向零件部訂貨<br />\n零件部又要向採購部落單<br />\n採購部再sourcing<br />\n咁大間公司 步驟咁繁複 經過咁多人<br />\n唔會依家裝完先有風聲傳出嚟<br />\n<br />\n大家諗下黨鐵係政府嘅<br />\n到依家舊款車嘅車廂都重係冇cam<br />\n黨鐵都未有 九巴就裝先 大家諗下合唔合理<br />\n依家香港周街都係cam 你避得晒咩？<br />\n最緊要保持警覺性 做好自己"},{"pid":"f0ea44b7574c54268d4434d278f0f22c843f162a","tid":1599553,"uid":14747,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"quote":{"pid":"70c3258554221e302f34f7f2895b283fa0c3df4c","tid":1599553,"uid":156632,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"23b684370e87010e89038244c00cd01b993e97d1","tid":1599553,"uid":14747,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T05:12:25.000Z","msg":"Live鏡頭只包車頭中間影出街果個，收音都係得一支，就係司機位對上<br />\n<br />\n利申 入面做的小薯"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T07:03:09.000Z","msg":"巴打可唔可出一出證件<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T07:34:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bfbb6d4df8d8a8630a6b817ca780b05ba94af996","tid":1599553,"uid":49329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T07:48:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e2b5193d821d82f3d20c31ad86cc82b4febee9e","tid":1599553,"uid":177213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"23b684370e87010e89038244c00cd01b993e97d1","tid":1599553,"uid":14747,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T05:12:25.000Z","msg":"Live鏡頭只包車頭中間影出街果個，收音都係得一支，就係司機位對上<br />\n<br />\n利申 入面做的小薯"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T07:48:41.000Z","msg":"大推有用情報<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n等我大大力錫巴打春袋先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hk